menu "LED Control Configuration"

    config LED_STRIP_GPIO
            int "GPIO number for the RGB LED"
            range 0 48
            default 48
            help
                The GPIO pin connected to the WS2812/NeoPixel LED. 
                Default is 48 on most ESP32-S3 DevKits.

        config LED_STRIP_BRIGHTNESS
            int "Maximum LED Brightness (0-255)"
            range 0 255
            default 50
            help
                Global brightness limit to prevent eye strain and high current draw.
                A value of 50 is usually sufficient for indoor use.

        config LED_ALARM_COLOR_RED
            int "Alarm Red Intensity"
            range 0 255
            default 255
            help
                Red component intensity during alarm blinks.

        config LED_ALARM_BLINK_SPEED_MS
            int "Alarm Blink Speed (ms)"
            default 200
            help
                Duration of the 'on' and 'off' phases during an alarm blink.

    endmenu